profile:
Award Winning Specialists!
416-236-8721

A&A Masonry is an award-winning Toronto based firm specializing in almost everything exterior.  Specialties include Stone work, Interlock, Interlocking, Paver stones, paving stones, Natural Stone, Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Masonry, brick repair, brick restoration, tuck pointing, waterproofing, foundation repairs, concrete steps, porches, walkways, caulking services (windows & doors), chimney repair and general exterior restorations for residential, commercial and industrial customers.

A&A is dedicated to providing the highest quality on every job. With a proud team of qualified artisans, we strive to complete every project in a timely and safe manner.

Our mission is to offer a unique and reliable service in anything Exterior within the Greater Toronto Area, differentiating ourselves from the competition by means of always delivering what we promise, on time and on budget.

Our commitment to excellence is our core value.
Customer satisfaction is our main goal, and we reach it every day by relying on our attention to customer service. By providing customized solutions for every job, we guarantee that we will never compromise on quality, safety and efficiency.

This approach together with our experience and knowledge allows us to effectively handle a wide variety of projects, from small to big, indoors or outdoors, renovations or repairs. 

We service:  Toronto, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Thornhill, Richmond Hill, York, North York, East York, Mimico, Hamilton, Brampton, Bolton and surrounding areas. 

For FREE ESTIMATE CALL: 416-236-8721

Being Masonry Contractors, Concrete Contractors, Stone  Contractors & Waterproofing Contractors we specialize in:
Stone work, Interlocking Natural Stone & Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Tuck Pointing, Chimney Repair, Chimney Rebuild, Chimney Restoration, tuckpointing, Brickwork, Brick Repair, Brick Replacement, Parging, Waterproofing, Foundation Repair, Concrete Resurfacing, Concrete Porches, Concrete Steps, Patios and Walkways, Flagstone, Cultured Stone, Caulking services (windows and doors), Masonry, Masonry repair, steps, concrete porches, concrete walkways and patios, caulking services.

profile:
Three Little Pigs Masonry provides expert masonry and concrete repairs, restoration and installation for the home and business owner.  
Our estimating department works as a team to find long term solutions and  help homeowners with many permanent solutions to their problems where other competitors have failed to succeed. Having over 45 years experience doesn't hurt either. 
The team at Three Little Pigs Masonry works together to provide the customer with a positive contractor experience from the first call to the last team member to leave your completed project. Most importantly,  you are dealing with actual MASONS from the management, the estimators and the crews on your property. 
No sales person will call and no high pressure sales pitch. Our warranties reflect the confidence Three Little Pigs Masonry provides.
Compare our warranties to those of our competitors. 
We are a family owned and operated business that prides itself  on the highest quality work and  providing exceptional customer service.

We specialize in STONE REFACING , structural masonry and concrete including underpinning and walk outs!
 
Here is a small list of our services: foundations, footings, pilings, parging, tuck pointing, concrete repair and restoration, concrete step repair, window sills, chimney repair and restoration, basement walkouts, flagstone, columns, pillars, patios, privacy walls, flagstone walkways, retaining walls, stone refacing, stone options to cover wood, stucco etc., waterproofing, underpinning, foundation repair, restoration- repair to stone, brick or block.
 
Please call us today!        

We're social here:

Beaver Paving Ltd. is a full service asphalt paving and Interlocking company. Established in 1980, Beaver  Paving Ltd. has been operating as family run business for over 35 years. With the original owner who continues to oversee and be involved with all aspects of the business, they have earned a reputation as being an exemplary company who excels in providing quality performance and customer service.
 
OUR GUARANTEE 
Beaver Paving Ltd ,we individually design and engineer your driveway using the highest quality materials combining expertise with experience. Although residential driveways and commercial lot designs and projects may vary from client to client, specifications and skill are always guaranteed to be consistent; from the biggest job to the smallest. 
Beaver Paving provides a full 12 month written guarantee with every contract.

*Residential Paving

profile:
At Tornado Plumbing we work hard to fulfill all your plumbing needs, and offer some of the best service in the GTA. Our products are high quality, and all of our work is under warranty. By using the most recent technology we can offer you the best service to ensure your plumbing work is done efficiently and with quality. We provide free estimates, competitive rates, and city rebates are available.
Our services include waterproofing, pipe burst, plumbing repairs, backwater valve, concrete work, water service and repairs, drain camera inspections, drain snaking, and underpinning (basement lowering).
With appointments booked at your convenience, and 24 hour emergency service, you’re sure to get the job done with Tornado Plumbing.

Check us out here:
https://www.facebook.com/TornadoPlumbingCom
https://twitter.com/TornadoPlumbing
https://www.instagram.com/tornado_plumbing/

YouTube videos on various plumbing and drain services may be found in our photo gallery.
services:
Waterproofing
Our skilled crews take all the necessary steps to clean and prepare your foundation wall prior to waterproofing.
We only use materials of the highest industry standard to seal your home from leaks.
With a 25 year warranty, you are guaranteed a dry basement and piece of mind.

Drains
When you need to replace your damaged sewer lines, we meet all city standards for drain work and backwater valves.
Using the minimally invasive pipe burst method, we can have your drains running again quickly.

Water Service
Using trench-less technology we can quickly replace your lead waterline or
upgrade your current water service, causing minimal damage to your property

Plumbing
We can take care of all your plumbing needs no matter the size.
Fixing small leaks to full plumbing line replacement, and everything in between.

Concrete work
From walkways to patio slabs we’ve got all your concrete needs covered.

Underpinning & Walkouts
If you’re looking for more living space, we can lower your basement to your desired height or add a second entrance.
Using approved engineer drawings, and following building codes, we will create the basement you want.

24/7 EMERGENCY SERVICE

The ROOTERWORX was established by a team that is experienced, skilled, and are in construction for decades. 

The head office of the ROOTERWORX is located in Mississauga and covers Toronto and GTA.
There are two divisions in our company for residential services: drain repair, catch basin cleaning, waterproofing, foundation & structural repair, concrete repair, concrete & foundation crack repair. 

And commercial services and multi-residential (apartment buildings, condominiums, commercial facilities): kitchen drain stack cleaning, negative side waterproofing, elevator shaft waterproofing, expansion joint waterproofing, ledge beam repair, concrete balcony repair, underground garage structural repair, underground garage waterproofing, underground garage concrete repair.

We have learned a lot through those years, and now we deliver the best to our customers.

Also, ROOTERWORX is open 24/7 for drain cleaning and drain repair services!

profile:
Toronto’s masonry professionals

GTA homeowners, property managers, and commercial building clients have come to rely on Avenue Road Masonry to provide the same professional standards of service and quality, that Avenue Road Roofing has provided for almost four decades.

Avenue Road Masonry is a professional Toronto brick masonry company that provides a variety of services involving brick repairs, replacements and installations.

Experienced and highly referenced; Avenue Road Masonry provides their clients the advantages of proven quality installation standards, full safety compliance and certifications, and competence with regard to chimney rebuilding, tuck-pointing, foundation waterproofing and heritage brick restoration; including stone work and fireplace construction and re-facing. profile:
City Wide Group is your first choice for waterproofing and underpinning service in Toronto & the GTA. We have been in business since 1961, building a reputation in this community for timely, quality work always done right the first time. Family owned and operated, our team of waterproofing and underpinning specialists is unmatched when it comes to client satisfaction. Our unwavering dedication to outstanding service has earned City Wide Group the prestigious Consumer’s Choice Award for 23 consecutive years.

***

For comprehensive waterproofing and underpinning solutions that protect your home, your equity and your peace of mind, choose City Wide Group.
Our expert advice and timely, dependable service are backed by an accurate quotation and guaranteed satisfaction, whatever your needs. We can permanently prevent wet basements, seal foundation cracks – inside and out, install weeping tiles, install drains inside or out and lower your basement.

***

Safeguard your family’s health, your most cherished possessions and your property’s value- contact City Wide Group today.

excellence - specializing in all facets of asphalt paving, concrete work and interlocking

industry.

Nortown Paving & Construction Inc. is a member of the Better Business Bureau and the Toronto Builders Association.

Our business is built on satisfied customers. All work carries a one year guarantee.

profile:
Toronto's Finest Concrete is a family owned and operated full service masonry and concrete company that is able to meet both the needs of the residential client and the commercial client who require complex applications of self-leveling cement for installation of hardwood, laminate, tile etc. For both, we provide quality workmanship done in a timely and effective manner, all the while creating an outstanding rapport to build lifelong relationships with our clients. It is our mission to provide expert quality, dependable and timely service that is done right the first time without compromising affordability. As third generation with a family history of over 40 years of expertise in the masonry and cement industry we are committed to continuing to serve our community and providing quality and affordability to all clients. You can have peace of mind and trust that we will treat your most valuable possessions and your property as we would our own with unparalleled service, quality and integrity.  We offer 10% Senior's Discount & Repeat Customer discounts to help give back to the community that has always given to us. 

Services Include:

*Concrete - patios, stairs, sidewalks/walkways, retaining walls & basement floors 

*Masonry/Brickwork - parging, tuckpointing, chimney's & all brick repair, coatings & applications 

*Waterproofing - leaky basements, damaged foundations walls, indoor/outdoor & weeping tile 

*Stone Work - includes flagstone, coping stone  interlock 

*Self-Leveling Cement - poured over damaged/cracked unlevel concrete substrates to create desired smooth & level finish 


Check Out Our Website - www.torontosfinestconcrete.ca

profile:
With decades of experience in the industry, our experts at Tikal Paving LTD have a reputation for designing and building beautiful, durable projects. We are your one-stop-shop for a variety of outdoor installation and repair services whether your needs are residential, commercial, industrial, or municipal.

Each project is carefully engineered to suit your individual needs and executed by our skilled and licensed contractors. Our team takes attention to detail seriously and uses top-quality materials for finished products that are as durable as they are visually appealing. That’s why any project completed by Tikal Paving LTD is guaranteed for one year. Our range of services includes landscaping, asphalt, concrete, interlocking brick, and snow plowing.

Our approach to outdoor projects is in our name; Tikal Paving. Tikal National Park is a 576 km² area in Guatemala that perfectly combines natural wonders with architectural feats that have survived enduring the elements for centuries. We believe the harmony between stunning natural landscaping and durable architectural elements is not only achievable, but a requirement for a functional and enjoyable space.

Not only do we guarantee superior workmanship, but we are also dedicated to providing the best customer service in the area. Get in touch with us to discuss your project and we will be happy to answer all your questions and provide a free quote.

profile:
Concrete Contractors
Landscape Construction

Pallotta Construction Ltd. was founded in 1977 and has a reputation for beautiful workmanship operating in the GTA and has maintained the same level of standards and service to this day. Paul Jr. oversees each job personally providing quotations and expertise on concrete, stonework, interlock, landscaping, waterproofing and drain.

CONCRETE:

A time-tested and true material, concrete can be used for the most high traffic areas around your home or formed into subtle outdoor accents. Driveways, curbs, sidewalks, accented porches or steps can all be poured and finished in a variety of ways. More industrial applications are also our speciality, from basement or garage floors to back entrances. We know concrete.
Applications

Driveways
Patios
Walkways
Curbs 	Porches
Steps
Swimming Pool Decks
Walkout Basements 	Garage Floors
Basement Floors
Slab on Grade

INTERLOCKING:

Give your driveway, steps, patio or walkway that time-worn feel of old Europe or turn your backyard into an elegant and relaxing space. Interlocking stone has no boundaries and gives us the ability to create an unlimited variety of geometric and random pattern designs. We are experts in the planning and installation of interlocking pavers, from traditional to modern.
Applications

Driveways
Patios
Walkways
Entrances 	Retaining Walls
Planters and Seat Walls
Swimming Pool Decks
Steps 

STONEWORK:

Earthy in colour and undoubtedly the most natural and durable of choices. Traditional random patterns or clean square-cut stone for a more elegant appearance can give any patio or walkway a timeless appeal. Natural stone over a poured concrete base has proven to be the strongest and longest-lasting of materials.
Applications

Patios
Walkways
Curbs 	Swimming Pool Decks
Overlays (over existing concrete porches or patios)
Random Flagstone
Square Cut Flagstone 

BUILD:

With an extensive background in concrete construction, we have the tools and knowledge necessary for any concrete application. From lowering a basement to gain valuable living space, pouring a new concrete floor, building basement walkouts or repairing a foundation leak - Pallotta construction knows concrete!
Applications

Basement Lowering
Basement Floors
Basement Entrances (Walkouts)
Underpinning
Bench Footings
Garage Floors 	Waterproofing
Interior Membrane
Weeping Tile
Sump Pits/Drain

profile:
At Sensational Stoneworks we consists of stone mason and concrete contractors that specialize in completing projects such as stone patios, porches, stairs, walkways, retaining walls and more! Our goal at Sensational Stoneworks is to ensure quality workmanship while using quality products. We take pride in our customer service and workmanship from beginning to end.

Installing stone patios, walls, stairs or other stone projects, can make a major difference in appearance and can also increase the value of your home.  There are many styles and colors to choose from. Styles can range from square cut, random flagstone, paving stones and more. We can provide samples and go over the many pamphlets in order to assist with the decision making process.

Our goal has always been to satisfy our customers. In this goal, we have been successful according to our wonderful reviews and many referrals. 

Call Us Today for your free consultation. We look forward to working with you.

647-351-0341 or info@sensationalstoneworks.ca
